<div id="c4">
<p>I was hanging out with my girlfriend&#8217;s sister recently.  The sister (21) looks, and behaves, like something straight out of The Hills.</p>

<p>She regaled us with tales of guys buying her drinks @ the airport on the way to visit us.</p>

<p>Some country musician even gave her a $300 belt buckle, making her pinky swear that she would promote his music in exchange.  (she rolls her eyes at this, as if she would ever lift her finger to promote anyone elses agenda)</p>

<p>I almost feel sorry for these women.  I really, really hope she cashes in on her looks (for her own sake) before they fade too much.  Normally I&#8217;m not a big fan of Schadenfreude, but sometimes it&#8217;s just too tempting.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by anonymous dude
